A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a vast underground network of glowing neon pipes and conduits in electric blue and magenta, carrying streams of luminescent data particles flowing through a complex industrial maze. In the foreground, a single pipe splits into multiple smaller channels that branch out like a river delta, with tiny glowing orbs traveling through the transparent tubes at different speeds. The architecture has an industrial brutalist feel with dark metal scaffolding and platforms, while holographic status indicators float near junction points. Steam and atmospheric haze catch the neon light, creating depth and mystery. The perspective is slightly elevated, looking down into this intricate delivery system where information flows continuously from source to destination through an elaborate choreography of pathways.
